"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該搞掂受天災戰亂所困既非洲班細佬仔<br />\n先好同我傳教,全能全善?連清除痛苦都無能力既神,你信埋佢啦</blockquote><br />\n雖然部份耶徒ok，但成日掛住傳教，十一奉獻整靚個教會，真人大愛問題又當冇事發生，現世都未搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11763b26245641e9bdb61611f8c6455833228086","tid":61102,"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次街邊比一堆傳教耶撚圍住，都覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話冇信仰就話你落地獄冇得上天堂，話信佛就同你講只有天父係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問佢哋信唔信陳雲，唔信都要落地獄，之後使套拳比佢睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.imgur.com/QNghOCD?r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.imgur.com%2FQNghOCD%3Fr&h=2043b100&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3060eee0a52532e111bf9f2dfe8df91e6ed57d64","tid":61102,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"我會送串佛珠畀你"},{"pid":"d530d02afcf5f5fd2250171eaf8983f1fcf46fae","tid":61102,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f914e61e603802b5dc09c70988f9a3d9932f668","tid":61102,"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次，我個frd 路過被幾條耶撚捉住咗，<br />\n佢唔走，仲要留喺到成粒鐘，畀埋電話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：好多次比幾個中年耶圍，我有潔癖好驚比人捉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 你個fd入左教十一奉獻左未"},{"pid":"17d00ab2417c0f2654e54e7ab3a154601495ef7e","tid":61102,"uid":56935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:35:37.000Z","msg":"收聲啦 耶穌佬"},{"pid":"28a9498a260f9351a81381130f5acf37922a44dd","tid":61102,"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會送串佛珠畀你</blockquote><br />\n真實對話<br />\n我：我佛教徒<br />\n耶：呢個世界只有一個神，其他都係假<br />\n我：點解要信神？我趕時間比返條路呀<br />\n耶：姐妹，信神先會得永生<br />\n我：不想永生，現世都咁痛苦，仲永生<br />\n耶：天堂會痛苦babababbabalalala<br />\n我：我真係好趕時間，你地比條路我<br />\n.........."},{"pid":"54c1142e8ef8a2b15f23e643d71d6c7acaf67899","tid":61102,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"傳教士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1813a0f6085b8bb964f872f1cbd1490c5c0b976f","tid":61102,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"我係某某區某某堂既教友<br />\nBelebelebababa <br />\n我教會方言<br />\n阿門<br />\n有事走先~拜～"},{"pid":"ff18221eb648f0bdfc55afdcf8b70c902fb87451","tid":61102,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74a3fe7a982946c99198c3f4a3ac08abe2cf7173","tid":61102,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"你病左  耶穌叫你祈禱就夠 <br />\n你被人哈 耶穌叫你祈禱就夠<br />\n面對世界上唔公平嘅事 耶穌叫你祈禱就夠<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咪就係得番你地班智陣先會繼續信"},{"pid":"fede476d86cee9dd449dc774bb733f059c188f4b","tid":61102,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你病左  耶穌叫你祈禱就夠 <br />\n你被人哈 耶穌叫你祈禱就夠<br />\n面對世界上唔公平嘅事 耶穌叫你祈禱就夠<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咪就係得番你地班智障先會繼續信</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3035d7c4363b61797da321fc8f32b60ab5837015","tid":61102,"uid":4973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"猶大?過得去啊,OK啦,如果佢唔出賣耶穌,耶穌就唔會釘十字架,佢唔釘十字架嘅話,咁你冇十字架攬,喂?你冇得撈㗎喎,你驚嘛?"},{"pid":"80edf0bd4b7766b0d3b98c71419e980a649dfb24","tid":61102,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},{"pid":"6a2a89d36d958da6f86830fed3353330e4a78eac","tid":61102,"u